---
import Layout from "../layouts/layout.astro";

import "../css/fonts/cooper.css";
---

<Layout title="Ben Borgers" background="#fff">
  <main class="home">
    <div class="home-grid">
      <aside class="portrait">
        <img
          src="/images/ben-sketch.png"
          alt="A hand-drawn sketch of Ben Borgers"
        />
      </aside>

      <div>
        <header class="masthead">
          <div>
            <h1
              class="nameplate"
              style="font-family: 'cooper';"
            >
              Ben Borgers
            </h1>
          </div>
        </header>

        <section class="home-copy">
          <p>
            I live in Boston and work at
            <a href="https://owner.com">Owner.com</a> as a
            <a href="https://www.owner.com/careers/role?=1912d8d8-b37f-4330-91ea-bb428d091322"
              >&ldquo;Product Builder&rdquo;</a
            >
            &mdash; a fancy name for being part software engineer, part product
            manager. Before that I was in
            college, and worked on product and engineering at
            <a href="https://buttondown.com">Buttondown</a>,
            <a href="https://notion.so/product">Notion</a>,
            <a href="https://locket.camera">Locket</a>,
            <a href="https://lu.ma">Luma</a>,
            <a href="https://glow.app">Glow</a>, and
            <a href="https://www.ibm.com/products/guardium">IBM</a>.
          </p>

          <p>
            I like making small, specific internet things. Some of them are
            serious tools, like
            <a href="https://opensheet.elk.sh">opensheet</a>, which turns
            public Google Sheets into an API and serves hundreds of millions of
            requests each month. Some are school-shaped, like
            <a href="/blocks">Blocks</a>,
            <a href="/wrapped">Tufts Meal Plan Wrapped</a>,
            <a href="https://ask.kiwi">Kiwi</a>, and JumboSmash. Some are just
            internet-shaped, like
            <a href="https://tiktokgraveyard.com">TikTok Graveyard</a>,
            <a href="https://igvalentine.com">IG Valentine</a>, and
            <a href="https://locketyearbook.com/kXYrENR6d1FPjUYYTDRI"
              >Locket Yearbook</a
            >.
          </p>

          <p>
            I studied computer science and engineering psychology at
            <a href="https://tufts.edu">Tufts University</a>, with a minor in
            German. I still have a soft spot for projects that feel like tiny
            institutions: <a href="https://bagel.institute">Bagel Institute</a>,
            <a href="https://war.elk.sh">War Room</a>,
            <a href="https://emojicdn.elk.sh">emojicdn</a>, and
            <a href="https://diffeqgrapher.com">diffeqgrapher.com</a> all live
            somewhere in that neighborhood.
          </p>

          <p>
            I would love to hear from you and grab coffee:
            <a href="mailto:benborgers@hey.com">benborgers@hey.com</a>.
          </p>
        </section>
      </div>
    </div>
  </main>
</Layout>

<style>
  .home {
    min-height: 100vh;
    padding: 3.5rem 1.5rem;
    color: black;
  }

  .home-grid {
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: 80px minmax(0, 1fr);
    column-gap: 1.5rem;
    row-gap: 2.5rem;
    max-width: 900px;
    margin: 0 auto;
  }

  .portrait {
    display: flex;
    justify-content: flex-end;
    padding-top: 1rem;
  }

  .portrait img {
    height: 6rem;
    width: auto;
    max-width: none;
    filter: grayscale(1);
  }

  .masthead {
    border-top: 1px solid black;
    padding-top: 0.75rem;
  }

  .nameplate {
    margin: 0;
    font-size: 28px;
    font-style: italic;
    font-weight: 400;
    line-height: 1;
  }

  .home-copy {
    max-width: 620px;
    margin-top: 2rem;
    font-size: 16px;
    line-height: 1.55;
    color: black;
  }

  .home-copy p {
    margin-block: 0 1.45rem;
  }

  .home-copy p:last-child {
    margin-bottom: 0;
  }

  .home-copy a {
    color: black;
    text-decoration-color: black;
    text-decoration-thickness: 1px;
    text-underline-offset: 0.18em;
  }

  @media (min-width: 640px) {
    .home-grid {
      grid-template-columns: 120px minmax(0, 1fr);
    }

    .portrait img {
      height: 8rem;
    }
  }

  @media (min-width: 768px) {
    .home {
      padding-top: 5rem;
      padding-bottom: 5rem;
    }

    .home-grid {
      grid-template-columns: 160px minmax(0, 1fr);
      column-gap: 2.5rem;
    }

    .portrait img {
      height: 10rem;
    }
  }
</style>
